<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,2006,2031]" lastBlockId="3.[151,1437,151,710]" lastPageId="3" pageId="2">
Adult rather small, 
<quantity box="[371,464,2007,2031]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="2" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4 mm</quantity>
long. Body mostly greyish pruinose with darkish spots. Front reddish-yellow but face and genae (cheeks) whitish. Mid-frontal stripe absent, ocellar area broadly triangular. Anepisternum bare; anepimeron with two strong setae. Wing very typical of 
<taxonomicName box="[825,943,185,210]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[825,943,185,210]" italics="true" pageId="3">Pherbellia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, with a dark reticulate pattern (the major character by which to distinguish the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Macquart, 1835" authorityName="Macquart" authorityYear="1835" box="[703,869,218,243]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Graphomyzina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[703,869,218,243]" italics="true" pageId="3">Graphomyzina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), costal area entirely black. Legs mainly dark or brownish; mid- and hind tibiae and tarsi medium red-orange. Male genitalia figured by 
<bibRefCitation author="Rozkosny" box="[1137,1331,252,277]" pageId="3" refString="Rozkosny, R. (1965) Die Revision der Sciomyziden (Diptera) aus den Sammlungen des National-Museums in Praha. Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae, 38, 633 - 649." type="journal article" year="1965">
Rozkošný (
<number box="[1265,1323,252,277]" pageId="3" value="1965.0">1965</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Vala" pageId="3" refString="Vala, J-C. (1989) Dipteres Sciomyzidae Euro-mediterraneens. Faune de France. France et Regions limitrophes. N ° 72. Federation Francaise des Societes des Sciences Naturelles, Paris, 300 pp + 9 pl." type="book" year="1989">
Vala (
<number box="[159,220,286,310]" pageId="3" value="1989.0">1989</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" type="distribution">
